data.description: Nestled in the tranquil countryside, this stunning ranch-style home offers 3 beds, 1.5 baths, and sits on 5.4 sprawling acres. Enjoy the serenity of pine-framed privacy and mesmerizing scenery from every bedroom window. With a fully renovated interior, an attached 2-car garage, and a spacious 30 x 20 heated pole barn, this property is a haven of modern comfort and rural charm. Additionally, this home is located in a school of choice area. Conveniently located about 10 miles from both Sebewaing and Caro. This home offers the perfect blend of country living and accessibility. Don't miss your opportunity to make this home your own. Schedule your private showing today.
